<li><i>Ermita a Parigi. Pagine autobiografiche</i>, <a href="/wiki/1994_in_literature" title="1994 in literature">1994</a> / <i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Hermit_in_Paris&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Hermit in Paris (page does not exist)">Hermit in Paris</a></i>, 2003</li>
