dit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Lorenzo Montano (page does not exist)">Lorenzo Montano</a> (1958) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><strong class="selflink">Italo Calvino</strong> (1959) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Enrico_Emanuelli&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Enrico Emanuelli (page does not exist)">Enrico Emanuelli</a> (1960) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Giorgio_Vigolo&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Giorgio Vigolo (page does not exist)">Giorgio Vigolo</a> (1961) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Giuseppe_Dess%C3%AC&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Giuseppe Dessì (page does not exist)">Giuseppe Dessì</a> (1962) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Ottiero_Ottieri&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Ottiero Ottieri (page does not exist)">Ottiero Ottieri</a> (1963) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Tommaso_Landolfi" title="Tommaso Landolfi">Tommaso Landolfi</a> (1964) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Biagio_Marin" title="Biagio Marin">Biagio Marin</a> (1965) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Manlio_Cancogni&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Manlio Cancogni (page does not exist)">Manlio Cancogni</a> (1966) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Primo_Levi" title="Primo Levi">Primo Levi</a> (1967) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Piero_Chiara" title="Piero Chiara">Piero Chiara</a> (1968) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/wiki/Niccol%C3%B2_Tucci" title="Niccolò Tucci">Niccolò Tucci</a> (1969) •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Alberto_Vigevani&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Alberto Vigevani (page does not exist)">Albe